HTML-Tooltip-Javascript version 0.01
========================

HTML::Tooltip::Javascript provides a perl interface 
for easy use of Walter Zorn's Javascript tooltip 
library.  See:

http://www.walterzorn.com/tooltip/tooltip_e.htm

It's intended for use in a web environment (e.g. in 
a cgi script running in a web browser), where Javascript 
is enabled.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Walter Zorn's Javascript Tooltip library, available at: http://www.walterzorn.com/tooltip/tooltip_e.htm

